INSERT INTO `field_data_body` (`entity_type`, `bundle`, `deleted`, `entity_id`, `revision_id`, `language`, `delta`, `body_value`, `body_summary`, `body_format`) VALUES ('node','page',0,1,1,'und',0,'<h1><strong>RESIDENTIAL ELECTRICAL</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family:open sans,arial,century gothic,sans-serif\">Unique Electric Services Inc.</span> has a long history in the commercial and industrial field. We are now offering that same level of service in the residential market. We have many service vehicles and master electrician that are on call 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. The next time a storm blows through and damages your incoming electrical service, call <span style=\"color:rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family:open sans,arial,century gothic,sans-serif\">Unique Electric Services Inc.</span> and we’ll have your power back on without delay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Electrical services upgrade from 60 Amps to 100 Amps and more</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>New house and town house wiring</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>New construction and renovations</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Trouble shooting</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Electrical repairs</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Circuit breakers and ballasts</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Electrical outlets and switches</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Computer cabling and data lines</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Lighting fixtures and ceiling fans</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Hot tub wiring</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>For all of your electrical needs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.uniqueelectricinc.ca/contact\">Call a Professional</a>, call UNIQUE ELECTRIC SERVICES INC.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>Electrical Contractors serving Edmonton and area</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>Call for free estimate by Master Electrician</strong></p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,2,2,'und',0,'<p><strong>You\'ve found professionals dedicated to your business.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to your business, timing is crucial. Thats why you can count on us for same day service. No matter how simple or complex your project, our licensed technicians are prepared to tackle your business problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New construction</li>\r\n	<li>New installations</li>\r\n	<li>High voltage work</li>\r\n	<li>Energy saving solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Computer cabling and data lines</li>\r\n	<li>Electric meter upgrades</li>\r\n	<li>Sub-panels</li>\r\n	<li>Security lighting</li>\r\n	<li>Panel upgrades</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>For all of your electrical needs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.uniqueelectricinc.ca/contact\">Call a Professional</a>, call UNIQUE ELECTRIC SERVICES INC.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>Electrical Contractors serving Edmonton and area</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><strong>Call for free estimate by Master Electrician</strong></p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,4,4,'und',0,'<p>A home remodeling or renovation job just isn’t complete without proper electrical rewiring and electric panel renovation. Having an up-to-date home electric system will secure your family’s safety and allow your more modern electrical appliances to run efficiently. The licensed, Insured and Master electricians at <strong>UNIQUE ELECTRIC SERVICES INC.</strong> specialize in most electrical renovations, including:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"rteindent4\">\r\n	<li>Basement Renovations</li>\r\n	<li>Bathroom Renovations</li>\r\n	<li>Kitchen Renovations</li>\r\n	<li>General House Renovations</li>\r\n	<li>Whole House Rewire</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Home Wiring</li>\r\n	<li>Knob &amp; Tube Rewire</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&